{"tid":2405094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權學堂：封區檢測如何侵犯人權？","createTime":"2021-02-12T06:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:20:55.000Z","uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7617a3766e747ca867d2f761ba7894f1881b670b","tid":2405094,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"【人權學堂：封區檢測如何侵犯人權？】<br />\n文章：<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org.hk/%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org.hk%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A0%2582%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ee89d689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org.hk/%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%AD%B8%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%EF%BC%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港第四波<del>新冠</del><span class=\"red\"><strong>武漢</strong></span>肺炎疫情反覆，政府自年初起實施突襲封區檢測政策，強制要求居民及逗留人士接受病毒檢測前，不得離開「受限區域」。然而有關做法不只屢遭社會各界抨擊勞民傷財，亦引發侵犯人身自由、知情權、私隱等多重人權疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n一、突襲封區奪知情權<br />\n二、勞工非自願缺勤遭減薪<br />\n三、破門執法侵犯私隱<br />\n四、少數族裔言語不通欠支援<br />\n五、穆斯林獲派豬肉食品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDCCaBb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDCCaBb.jpg&h=ea5c209c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UroE8nW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUroE8nW.jpg&h=6101fc16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vS4haBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvS4haBi.jpg&h=0f8e92cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMNq3Wm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMNq3Wm.jpg&h=9979c022&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PahCaBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPahCaBo.jpg&h=07aeef5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGq8hgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGq8hgq.jpg&h=7adb05e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2JhU26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2JhU26.jpg&h=25a7c480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnRWq9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnRWq9P.jpg&h=d0f6416d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JdecPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JdecPQ.jpg&h=26c009dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X1vvBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X1vvBw.jpg&h=e53d95a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource : #國際特赦組織香港分會<br />\n#林鄭食屎狗 #柒婆冚家剷 #武漢肺炎 #支那病毒 #支共禍患 #禍港正苦 #封區 #封區唔封關 #勞民傷財 #人禍比天災更可怕"}]}